Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早起的感觉还真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了、来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…啊，是Liki呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.98,0:02:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭?去、我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我今天整天都没事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在?太早了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.43,0:02:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是才一大早…啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.10,0:02:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍…晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.94,0:02:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五话 假日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.55,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天都被我给睡掉了 实在太失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.35,0:02:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然休息了这么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:02:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天服务台的工作就不会打瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…难得的假日耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.86,0:03:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别难过别难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你一家好吃的店 你就快打起精神来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.40,0:03:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的店?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，谢谢你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，要各付各的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.72,0:03:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!好像很贵的店耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是才刚领薪水吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.39,0:03:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶而也该小小奢侈一下让自己更像女人才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.87,0:03:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本餐厅不招待未成年的消费者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的同事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说，你们是要挑客人啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，绝对没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liki，我到其他的店也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.99,0:04:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临，请让两位进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.43,0:04:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了，欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.43,0:04:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗，今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一般的客人离开反而会引人注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.84,0:04:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…别忘了，要化解紧张的气氛\N还是得靠一些鲜花来点缀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.92,0:04:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是有点便宜的花…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候大驾光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内线交易?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.30,0:04:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们Aineias对于经济活动的管制不是很宽松吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.57,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有些恶劣的避险基金集团\N企图跟『微笑侏儒』勾结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.74,0:04:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『微笑侏儒』?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.14,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个将经济界的幕后情报\N当作商品交易的地下组织对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.91,0:05:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来打算等查出特定地点后就加以一网打尽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.11,0:05:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是目前还没有任何情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.05,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当都市繁荣起来之后\N黑社会的勾结也更加的复杂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就不再那么单纯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是人世间…或是人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，气氛实在是大棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧，我是不是也该找Lumiere一起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.97,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系…每天都见面\N偶尔也该轻松一下才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.64,0:05:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没·有·错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有找Eclair小姐来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.29,0:05:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定也希望难得的假日\N可以过着看不到我的一天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.13,0:05:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她对歌剧有兴趣的话 我就会邀请她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，我出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.97,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.07,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好好吃喔！ 我要开动啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不怎么样的菜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能满意那真是我的荣幸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.45,0:06:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老哥们也算是多角化经营啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下的根部扎实的话 地上就会草木繁盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.89,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有句话说樱花之下什么什么的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.66,0:06:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…能有这么可靠的朋友\N我真是太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，吃得好撑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你的魅力都吃掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，冰淇淋是放在另一个胃里的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.78,0:06:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以邀您跳支舞吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.42,0:06:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃，好幸福哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.26,0:07:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因为带了小鬼所以都没人来搭讪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?你刚刚说了什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛…不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.71,0:07:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.38,0:07:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，这样看起来比较像大人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.22,0:07:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我会很头痛的啦，Liki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.22,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系…还亏你每天口红不离身呢\N根本就没看你再用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.46,0:07:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂上口红的话要控制力量就很困难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.13,0:07:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.77,0:07:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起勇气来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以邀您跳支舞吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.25,0:07:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.05,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意我，你就快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.05,0:07:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是头一次跳舞吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.54,0:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么?炸弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是地震耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是绝对不会让我们的朋友受伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这句话可真是让人安心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然，这样果然麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在发抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害怕刚刚的地震吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉我你的名字吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E…Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…闪电…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.19,0:09:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信…命运吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.09,0:09:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.30,0:09:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙浩瀚、人生苦短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.87,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们应该珍惜\N上帝赐予我们的这场命运邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.21,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…别这样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙搞什么?抄家伙了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…您误会了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.22,0:09:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必找借口了我就知道会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.50,0:09:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.70,0:09:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.34,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，这衣服还是新的耶～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙也是敌人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造人?有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair你在哪里？Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.91,0:10:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱尔普夏芙特的茶花公主好久没看了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妈妈走散了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了，听姐姐的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非法的改造人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.47,0:12:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受雇的保镖吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.58,0:12:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到那家餐厅\N竟然是掩护地下情报交易的场所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.15,0:12:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你们的福 害得我难得的假日泡汤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里本来是个不错的藏身地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 我们的餐厅也完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.49,0:12:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且连跟对方的契约也… 全都泡汤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.09,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说清楚哦 我又不是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正双方本来就有打算要趁机黑吃黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢，你害得我所有计画都被打乱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.01,0:12:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然要你赔偿我才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.04,0:12:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是我很穷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还连劳保都没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.52,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你用你的身体来还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里看来并不像是小学露营嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来『微笑侏儒』那群混球把我们给出卖了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.27,0:13:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?那这艘船不就也有可能被盯上了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再不快点把货送到处理设施去的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理设施?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.12,0:14:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发时间好像提前了立刻作好起飞的准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发?起飞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙港！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已经开战了自然就要先下手为强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要在第一时间攻击对方的运输船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…里面的货是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.76,0:14:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们拐走了上流社会的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.33,0:14:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在他们的潜意识里施于深层催眠的暗示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗示虽然不会马上表现出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.06,0:14:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是经过一段时间之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会完全听从组织的话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这些小孩子再去诱拐其他的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时式的暗示催眠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.98,0:15:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这些孩子们变成大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为社会上的统治阶层之一时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗示要是启动的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会乖乖听从组织的话是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是个相当远大的计画呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.09,0:15:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过效果的确惊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财经界的高官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.53,0:15:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，搞不好连一国之君\N都有可能会成为自己的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个相当不错的计画呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.03,0:15:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要从中夺们是打算走这项计划吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都没有想过要放他们回家吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.08,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你愿意替我工作的话\N刚刚的事情就一笔勾销了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.68,0:15:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还会提供你其他的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对…我会尽棉薄之力的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.80,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都被我知道了\N那我就更不能自己一个人逃跑了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是在突袭“吹笛手”之城吧？\N(注：通话“魔法的吹笛手”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是小型的空降打击机部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点应战 快点准备起飞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看货物有没有异常 快点去确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.61,0:16:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门弹开了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.39,0:16:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，快回原来的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.02,0:16:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，小孩子就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，不要找我麻烦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.87,0:17:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哭泣的小孩总是容易让人失去戒心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.22,0:17:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这离优雅还真是差了一大截呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骇了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.07,0:17:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人透过卫星网络对我们进行骇客攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点调查入侵来源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.91,0:17:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来回敬他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们守不住了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，发生了什么事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程式入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么有人和某位小姐这么像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩到底想怎样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.69,0:19:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在干什么，快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是她们两个的身分保证人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被加了暗示催眠的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.73,0:19:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经送到医院去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.26,0:19:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止被处理过的孩子名单\N也已经交给有关当局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.57,0:19:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过追踪调查所有孩子的暗示应该都能解开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.01,0:20:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位 真是连放假都得要麻烦你们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.21,0:20:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，lair她人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.68,0:20:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.18,0:20:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.95,0:20:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的令人怀念的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.49,0:20:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁星们在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，miere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.67,0:20:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听的歌呢 从哪里学来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说天晓得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就唱出来了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.24,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，别哭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.31,0:20:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈马上就来接你了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，别哭嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.98,0:20:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继续唱歌给你听喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁星们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还蛮投入的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.39,0:20:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灌注於心里的摇篮曲
